    <head><lb ed="X" n="0501c05"/>　　　　<persName key="A014317">僧伽</persName>傳</head>
    <p><anchor n="X.77.1524.0501c06"/><lb ed="X" n="0501c06"/><persName key="A014317">僧伽</persName>。姓吳氏。名<persName key="A014317">文祐</persName>。宋初<placeName key="PL000000019154">信豐</placeName>人。止於縣<placeName key="unknown">明覺院</placeName>。舉
        <lb ed="X" n="0501c07"/>止跌宕。人目為狂。甞書松柏上曰。趙家天子趙家王。
        <lb ed="X" n="0501c08"/>言趙氏方興。如松柏之茂也。縣民<persName key="unknown">曾氏</persName>老無嗣。知<persName key="A014317">僧<lb ed="X" n="0501c09"/>伽</persName>有異。設飯禮之。未及召。黎明排闥入。<persName key="unknown">曾氏</persName>膳甚豐。
        <lb ed="X" n="0501c10"/><persName key="A014317">僧伽</persName>曰。當以珠報。曾果得二子。學佛者<persName key="unknown">孫德</persName>。自汀之
        <lb ed="X" n="0501c11"/><placeName key="PL000000018005">南安</placeName>。謁<persName key="unknown">定應</persName>禪師。曰。<placeName key="PL000000019272">雩都</placeName>有人。禮我何為。孫不悟。曰。
        <lb ed="X" n="0501c12"/><persName key="A014317">僧伽</persName>吾法子也。孫告歸。師持一扇付孫曰。為寄<persName key="A014317">僧伽</persName>。
        <lb ed="X" n="0501c13"/>舟將抵邑。<persName key="A014317">僧伽</persName>候之。邀曰。我師扇安在。孫以扇付之
        <lb ed="X" n="0501c14"/>莫能欺。一日昏暮詣寺中闔戶。趺坐而化。葢<date from-iso="1009-07-01" to-iso="1009-07-30" key="j20897712089800">祥符己<lb ed="X" n="0501c15"/>酉六月</date>日也。</p>
